Some are born
to endless night.

607
01:16:45,213 --> 01:16:47,477
Well, Rome weren't built
in a day, Cole.

608
01:16:47,582 --> 01:16:50,881
Course, uh, I wasn't
overseein' that particular job.

609
01:17:24,119 --> 01:17:26,781
